item.description:
Not many good weather days left, so we'll try to squeeze in a few more tennis outings. It will be good weather on Sunday (66 degrees & sunny). We will hit around and maybe play some games if so desired. Please indicate your level in your RSVP. Hope you can make it. All levels welcome.

The tennis courts are in the back of the mall - bear right of the mall to get to Arsenal Park.

If you need a ride, please indicate the town and/or T stop you are coming from. Our members may be able to give you a ride.
